00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:07,620
about World War I. The so-called, Great War?

3
00:00:07,620 --> 00:00:11,960
World War I wasn’t the most destructive
war, or the first total war, and it certainly

4
00:00:11,968 --> 00:00:17,030
wasn’t - despite its billing - the war to
end all wars. But it was the war to change

5
00:00:17,030 --> 00:00:21,780
all wars. World War I changed our outlook,
it normalized cynicism and irony, which, I

6
00:00:21,780 --> 00:00:25,880
think you’ll agree, are kind of dominant lenses for
describing our world today. Basically, I’d argue

7
00:00:25,879 --> 00:00:30,960
